>&nbsp;Self-assessment</h2>
<p local-id=3D"b961a5475b8c">Start by thinking through your existing streng=
ths and development areas. What are you really good at? Where could you imp=
rove? This will help you figure out what to target. Look at past performanc=
e reviews for inspiration, or reach out to the people you work with closely=
 for feedback.</p>
