allback%3D%22%F0%9F%8E%AF%22+%2F%3E">&nbsp;Goals</h2>
<p local-id=3D"a93873560a83">Choose SMART goals for your growth: they shoul=
d be <strong>S</strong>pecific, <strong>M</strong>easurable, <strong>A</str=
ong>chievable, <strong>R</strong>elevant, and <strong>T</strong>ime-bound. =
Keep the number of goals low and track opportunities that will help you ach=
ieve the goals you set. If you're not sure where to start, look at your gro=
wth areas from the previous section.</p>
